ischen Humanismus an der Schwelle zur Moderne, entwickelt er Konsequenzen für ein Erkenntnisprogramm, das dem Humanismus erneute Geltung und kulturelle Orientierungskompetenz verschaffen kann.  aWhat role can and should humanism play in the Era of Globalization?Hilmar Kallweit critically discusses and reconstructs the sustainability of anthropological and ethical explanatory schemes which have been guiding humanism since ancient times.Using pertinent sources from the two main phases of post-classical humanism, rhetorical humanism of the early modern era, and classical humanism on the threshold of modernity, he develops implications for an awareness program, which can provide humanism with renewed validity and cultural orientation skills.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aHumanismxHistory. 0aHumanism. 4aAnthropologie. 4aEthik. 4aGlobalisierung. 4aKultur. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aMensch. 4aPhilosophiegeschichte. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aCultural Studies.  aCultural Theory.  aCulture.  aGlobalization.  aHistory of Philosophy.  aHuman.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2014z9783110370416oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014z9783111025223oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383762579040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839425794?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.de